@achalshah20 Actually there is a problem in converting the frozen.pb file( generated after freeze_graph.py) to optimize inference file so it can be deployed on Android.

node {
  name: "output/predictions"
  op: "ArgMax"
  input: "output/scores"
  input: "output/predictions/dimension"
  attr {
    key: "T"
    value {
      type: DT_FLOAT
    }
  }
  attr {
    key: "Tidx"
    value {
      type: DT_INT32
    }
  }
  attr {
    key: "output_type"
    value {
      type: DT_INT64
    }
  }
}
